{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893434299,"sessionID":"ses_28486105affee2QiTZn90dNmET","part":{"id":"prt_d7b7e3d650014sdxXMpXgcAm7R","messageID":"msg_d7b7e25230011RF86CDiWZknV3","sessionID":"ses_28486105affee2QiTZn90dNmET","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_6fb8723196b040bda00f078d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-040: Python SDK/CLI 测试 — Tasks\n\n**Module:** `sdk-python/tests` | **Language:** Python | **Size:** M\n**Base specs:** `python-sdk/agentcube/`, `python-sdk/tests/` source code\n**Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n\n---\n\n## T-1: Fix existing test bugs and failing tests\n\n- [ ] Fix `test_code_interpreter.py` — rename 3 methods in `TestStop` class to add `test_` prefix: `stop_closes_dp_client` → `test_stop_closes_dp_client`, `stop_deletes_session` → `test_stop_deletes_session`, `stop_closes_cp_client` → `test_stop_closes_cp_client`\n- [ ] Fix `test_control_plane.py` — 5 failing tests in `TestCreateSession` and `TestSessionReuse` (mock `session.post` returns dict instead of Response object with `.json()` method)\n- [ ] Fix `test_data_plane.py` — `test_request_url_construction` failing (mock `session.request` kwargs mismatch: `url` key missing)\n- [ ] Run `pytest python-sdk/tests/ -v` — verify all existing tests pass (172 tests, 0 failures)\n\n---\n\n## T-2: Extend `test_code_interpreter.py` — CodeInterpreterClient gaps\n\n- [ ] `test_stop_when_session_id_is_none` — session_id=None → skips delete_session, still closes dp and cp clients\n- [ ] `test_stop_when_dp_client_not_initialized` — no dp_client attribute → no crash (hasattr guard)\n- [ ] `test_stop_when_cp_client_not_initialized` — no cp_client attribute → no crash (hasattr guard)\n- [ ] `test_stop_idempotent` — multiple stop() calls → each cleanup action called exactly once\n- [ ] `test_run_code_python3_language` — `\"python3\"` → writes .py file + executes via python3\n- [ ] `test_run_code_py_language` — `\"py\"` → writes .py file + executes via python3\n- [ ] `test_run_code_case_insensitive` — `\"PYTHON\"` → writes .py file + executes via python3\n- [ ] `test_run_code_passes_timeout_to_execute` — `timeout=30.0` → passed through to execute_command\n- [ ] `test_run_code_unsupported_language` — `\"ruby\"` → raises `ValueError(\"Unsupported language: ruby\")`\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_with_list_input` — `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]` → passed as-is to dp (not double-wrapped)\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_empty_string` — `\"\"` → `[\"\"]` sent to dp\n- [ ] `test_session_created_flag_true_when_no_session_id` — `_session_created=True` when session_id=None\n- [ ] `test_session_created_flag_false_when_session_id_provided` — `_session_created=False` when session_id provided\n- [ ] `test_data_plane_init_failure_deletes_session` — DP init raises → delete_session called, session_id=None, exception re-raised\n- [ ] `test_data_plane_init_failure_no_cleanup_for_reused_session` — `_session_created=False` + DP init fails → no delete_session, exception re-raised\n- [ ] `test_data_plane_init_called_with_correct_params` — session_id, router_url, namespace, cr_name passed to DP constructor\n\n---\n\n## T-3: Extend `test_data_plane.py` — CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient gaps\n\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_http_error_propagates` — HTTP 500 → raise_for_status propagates HTTPError\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_timeout_buffer_explicit` — `timeout=30` → request timeout tuple `(connect_timeout, 32.0)`\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_timeout_buffer_default` — `timeout=None`, default 120 → request timeout `(connect_timeout, 122.0)`\n- [ ] `test_execute_command_timeout_string_in_body` — body `timeout` field is `\"30s\"` (original value, not buffered)\n- [ ] `test_write_file_http_error_propagates` — HTTP error → raise_for_status propagates\n- [ ] `test_write_file_unicode_content` — Unicode string → base64 encoded correctly in JSON body\n- [ ] `test_write_file_empty_content` — empty string → base64 of `\"\"` sent\n- [ ] `test_upload_file_session_header_present` 